article.description: — Sam Griffin had 20 points as Tulsa edged past Southern Illinois 69-65 on Saturday.
article.headline: Griffin scores 20 to carry Tulsa past S. Illinois 69-65
article.linkText: Griffin scores 20 to carry Tulsa past S. Illinois 69-65
article.story: TULSA, Okla. -- — Sam Griffin had 20 points as Tulsa edged past Southern Illinois 69-65 on Saturday. Jeriah Horne had 15 points for Tulsa (5-5). Tim Dalger added 12 points. Ben Coupet Jr. tied a career high with 27 points for the Salukis (5-4). Marcus Domask added 16 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
